  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The efficacy of eribulin is now well known in metastatic breast cancer. Furthermore, a phase
      III combine study ( chemo + bev)in metastatic first line shown a gain in PFS with no extra
      toxicities.

      It could be interesting to explore the combination of bev + eribulin in first line metastatic
      breast cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
